  "text": "Functional outcomes included a participant-reported questionnaire regarding the ability to speak, chew and swallow [CITATION_1] ; a 10-point VAS on both perceived global reduction in activities of daily living and the ability to chew and swallow [CITATION_2] . One study used a speech test where the phoneme sequence PUTTICA was repeated as many times as possible over a 2-min period [CITATION_3] .",
